reviewText: Wow. Um. So this video is insane. It's meant to be funny, but all of the jokes fall flat. It's the insane editing and awkward pacing and just overall chaotic nature of the people involved that makes this hilarious. It's very similar to How Can I Tell If I'm ^Really^ In Love in terms of cohesiveness. There's something in the teeth that these people wear. It's potent. Who needs hallucinogenic drugs when you have this VHS tape?
